  "detailed_description": "<strong>Tipsy Woods</strong> is a retro style Horror game, where a players must navigate a forest. Armed only with a flashlight and limited stamina, you'll scour the woods in search of 8 bottles while evading the ever-watchful beast. Stay vigilant as day turns to night, relying on scattered batteries to keep your flashlight lit. But beware: the forest is rife with chilling encounters, from jump scares to sinister environmental traps. Can you outsmart the monster and survive the nightmarish forest?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Flash Light Battery</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995220/extras/c4207ba5f282472723527bdf6b61bd31.poster.avif?t=1766847586\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995220/extras/c4207ba5f282472723527bdf6b61bd31.webm?t=1766847586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995220/extras/c4207ba5f282472723527bdf6b61bd31.mp4?t=1766847586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Your flashlight is your lifeline, but each beam drains its battery. Find scattered replacements to keep the darkness at bay and survive the nightmarish forest.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >8 Bottles</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995220/extras/2c6d51757573a4fd8ef7c709e804425d.poster.avif?t=1766847586\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995220/extras/2c6d51757573a4fd8ef7c709e804425d.webm?t=1766847586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995220/extras/2c6d51757573a4fd8ef7c709e804425d.mp4?t=1766847586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Collect and consume 8 bottles to escape the forest's clutches and emerge victorious in this chilling adventure.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Running & Stamina</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995220/extras/111368a5ab25d7b60278a9585f38180e.poster.avif?t=1766847586\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995220/extras/111368a5ab25d7b60278a9585f38180e.webm?t=1766847586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995220/extras/111368a5ab25d7b60278a9585f38180e.mp4?t=1766847586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Running consumes stamina in your desperate bid for survival, but halt to replenish your strength and outlast the forest's relentless horrors.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995220/extras/b46cba1441863e4df93f03ed58248143.poster.avif?t=1766847586\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995220/extras/b46cba1441863e4df93f03ed58248143.webm?t=1766847586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995220/extras/b46cba1441863e4df93f03ed58248143.mp4?t=1766847586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore diverse locales from wheat fields to ominous barns, each harboring its own secrets.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Monster</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995220/extras/85e24d6fceb70951f1d39aea2745b73b.poster.avif?t=1766847586\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995220/extras/85e24d6fceb70951f1d39aea2745b73b.webm?t=1766847586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995220/extras/85e24d6fceb70951f1d39aea2745b73b.mp4?t=1766847586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Beware the monster that roams the forest.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Encounters </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995220/extras/111368a5ab25d7b60278a9585f38180e.poster.avif?t=1766847586\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995220/extras/111368a5ab25d7b60278a9585f38180e.webm?t=1766847586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995220/extras/111368a5ab25d7b60278a9585f38180e.mp4?t=1766847586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Discover eerie encounters like an old music player haunting the woods, its melodies masking sinister secrets waiting to be uncovered in the darkness.",
